title: QUIZ: Drake Lyric Or 18th Century Poem?
text:
QUIZ: Drake Lyric Or 18th Century Poem? This is way harder than it sounds. Aaron Barksdale Voices Editorial Fellow, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/24/2015 10:13 AM EDT 
Drake is well-known for his soft, sensitive lyrics and R&B vocals from hits like "Take Care" and "Hold On, We're Going Home." In honor of his 28th birthday we want to test your your knowledge. 
Can you guess if the following lines are lyrics are from a Drake song or a line from a William Blake poem? 
Take the quiz below!
